data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2.5-bath home nestled in a quiet cul de sac with a greenbelt lot and no rear neighbors. Enjoy the open floorplan, upgraded flooring, and a spacious master bedroom featuring a sitting area and large closet. Upstairs, find a versatile loft and all bedrooms. Don't miss the fantastic amenity center with a pool, basketball, and playground! This home truly has everything you need for comfortable living both inside and out.
